    <artifactId>truevfs-driver-tar-gzip</artifactId>

    <name>TrueVFS Driver TAR.GZIP</name>
    <description>
        The file system driver for GZIP compressed TAR files.
        Files of this type typically have the extension tar.gz, tar.gzip
        or .tgz.

        Add the JAR artifact of this module to the run time class path to
        make its file system drivers available for service location in the
        client API modules.
    </description>

